<headline>Severe Weather Statement issued May 06 at 10:29PM EDT until May 07 at 12:00AM EDT by NWS Blacksburg</headline>
<description>...THE SEVERE THUNDERSTORM WARNING FOR EAST CENTRAL PITTSYLVANIA AND
NORTHWESTERN HALIFAX COUNTIES WILL EXPIRE AT 1030 PM EDT...
The severe thunderstorm which prompted the warning has weakened.
Therefore, the warning will be allowed to expire.
A Tornado Watch remains in effect until midnight EDT for north
central North Carolina...central, south central and west central
Virginia...and south central Virginia.</description>
